article_title: UnitedHealth Group Earnings: What to Watch
article_text:
UnitedHealth Group Inc. is scheduled to announce its fourth-quarter earnings before the market opens Tuesday. Here’s what you need to know:

EARNINGS FORECAST: Net income of $1.38 a share for the fourth quarter is the consensus of analysts surveyed by Thomson Reuters, compared with $1.55 reported a year earlier. UnitedHealth on Nov. 19 downgraded its earnings projection for 2015, based on problems with its business on the...
